PersonalMission.Name: SPG-3: Slow and Steady Gets Stunned
PersonalMission.Description: Concealed and powerful enemy tank destroyers and well-armored heavy tanks can easily turn the tide of the battle. They are the first-priority targets, and causing damage to them (or assisting in their destruction) should be the primary objective for a player in an SPG. The majority of heavies and tank destroyers are slow and hulking, which increases the chances for a successful shot.

Primary.Conditions: Stun heavy tanks or tank destroyers 4 times
